      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "こんな状態じゃ、見せ場の撮影なんて\nとても無理ですよ～",
      "startTime": 6.466666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "今までのシーンだって\nなんとかOKをもらえてただけですし",
      "startTime": 10.5678004865293,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "確かにリテイクは多かったけど\n出来は凄くよかったぞ？",
      "startTime": 16.033333333333335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 17.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "そうでしょうか……？\n私は全然自信ないです……う～ん",
      "startTime": 20.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "渚、ちょっと気晴らしに散歩でもしないか？",
      "startTime": 25.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 28.966666666666665
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "え？　散歩？",
      "startTime": 28.966666666666665,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3800.000000000001,
          "startTime": 32.766666666666666
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3200.00000173847,
          "startTime": 32.166666668405135
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 32.13333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 32.13333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "海がとっても綺麗ですよねぇ～\n確かに気分転換にはちょうどいいかも……って、あれ？",
      "startTime": 36.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 42.63333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ……これって、サンドアート？",
      "startTime": 42.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 46.766666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃達が休憩時間のたびに\nちょっとずつ作ってたみたいだな",
      "startTime": 49.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "えっ琴乃ちゃん達が？\nなんで私に内緒で……？",
      "startTime": 54.233333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 56.833333333333336
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "ずるいです\n私もみんなと一緒に作りたかったのに",
      "startTime": 58.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 61.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "……あ、砂に何か文字が書いてある……？",
      "startTime": 61.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 66.36666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "『芽衣は渚ちゃんのダンスがすっごい好きだよ！』\nこれって……私宛てのメッセージ、ですか？",
      "startTime": 72.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03-ngs011.m4a",
      "text": "これは沙季ちゃんから\nあ、これはすずちゃんだ。ふふ、もう……",
      "startTime": 79.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 85.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03-ngs012.m4a",
      "text": "『渚なら大丈夫。頼りにしてるから』\n琴乃ちゃん……",
      "startTime": 90.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "みんな渚の頑張りに影響を受けて\nそれぞれ自主練を頑張ってたんだ",
      "startTime": 95.1749999523163,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 97.76666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03-ngs013.m4a",
      "text": "そう……だったんですか",
      "startTime": 97.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03-ngs014.m4a",
      "text": "確かにみんな……レッスンのたびに凄く上達してて\n毎回びっくりしてたんです",
      "startTime": 105.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 108.03333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03-ngs015.m4a",
      "text": "でも、なんでみんなわざわざメッセージをここに？\n直接言ってくれればいいのに",
      "startTime": 112.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "言ってたさ\nでも、みんなの声に耳を傾ける余裕がなかっただろ？",
      "startTime": 117.537149953221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 121.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03-ngs016.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば……\nみんな何度も声を掛けてくれてました",
      "startTime": 123.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03-ngs017.m4a",
      "text": "でも、何を言われても耳をすり抜けちゃって\n琴乃ちゃんの言葉も……",
      "startTime": 131.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 133.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "だからこうして\n違う形で励まそうと思ったんだろうな",
      "startTime": 134.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03-ngs018.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、私のことをこんなに考えてくれて……",
      "startTime": 137.73333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 142.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03-ngs019.m4a",
      "text": "私、まだまだですね\nみんなの気持ちに気付けていませんでした",
      "startTime": 146.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（どこか吹っ切れたこの表情……もう、心配ないかな）",
      "startTime": 149.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03-ngs020.m4a",
      "text": "あっ！　波が……",
      "startTime": 155.83333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03-ngs021.m4a",
      "text": "ああ～、流されちゃった……\n写真撮っておけばよかったなぁ",
      "startTime": 161.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03-ngs022.m4a",
      "text": "でも、元気を沢山もらえました\n{user}さん、ありがとうございます",
      "startTime": 167.83333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03-ngs023.m4a",
      "text": "私、みんなの背中をとにかく追いかけなきゃって焦って\n周りが見えなくなってました",
      "startTime": 174.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_02_03-ngs024.m4a",
      "text": "私の隣には月ストのみんながいる……\nそう思ったら凄く楽になりました",
      "startTime": 180.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
